{"talk":{"id":64836,"name":"Thomas Abt: Why violence clusters in cities -- and how to reduce it","description":"Reducing violence in cities in the US isn't the impossible, intractable challenge many believe it to be, says crime researcher and educator Thomas Abt. He explains how urban violence is \"sticky\" -- meaning that it clusters among a surprisingly small number of people and places -- and presents an innovative, targeted strategy to make our cities safer, right now, without big budgets or new laws.","slug":"thomas_abt_why_violence_clusters_in_cities_and_how_to_reduce_it","recorded_at":"2020-03-04 00:00:00","published_at":"2020-07-13 19:30:27","updated_at":"2021-04-09 19:44:30","viewed_count":0,"emailed_count":0,"event":{"id":643,"name":"TEDMED 2020"},"images":[{"image":{"size":"113x85","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2a335990c2c23bb044429c6c39bc58eb0139f89f_113x85.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"240x180","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2a335990c2c23bb044429c6c39bc58eb0139f89f_240x180.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"615x461","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2a335990c2c23bb044429c6c39bc58eb0139f89f_615x461.jpg"}},{"image":{"size":"2400x1800","url":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/2a335990c2c23bb044429c6c39bc58eb0139f89f_2400x1800.jpg"}}],"image_16x9":"https:\/\/pe.tedcdn.com\/images\/ted\/5775ca19a0d4ea8ea2b6731322562f8793eb28ca_2880x1620.jpg","media":{"internal":{"64k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/ThomasAbt_2020P-64k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":7333594,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"180k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/ThomasAbt_2020P-180k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":20345745,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"320k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/ThomasAbt_2020P-320k.mp4?apikey=c692baa7dafbf74e4fbde1ac88b44cafc96cfe7a","filesize_bytes":35998544,"mime_type":"video\/mp4"},"450k":{"uri":"https:\/\/download.ted.com\/talks\/Tho